=rbac_assets


Based on rbac_snippets, is an extension for Radiant CMS that utilizes the extension RBAC_Base to allow only users in the "Assets" role to edit assets. If you do not have the rbac_base extension installed it will raise a RbacSnippetsExtension::MissingRequirement exception when activated.

See http://ext.radiantcms.org/extensions/87-rbac_base

Truly the credit for this extension goes to Jim Gay at http://www.saturnflyer.com


---------------------------------------

First Install the rbac_base extension from the Radiant CMS extension repository then:

 'rake radiant:extensions:rbac_base:migrate'
 'rake radiant:extensions:rbac_base:update'


Install rbac_assets and run migration and update tasks:

'rake radiant:extensions:rbac_assets:migrate'
'rake radiant:extensions:rbac_assets:update'


Restart server





  
